          Upupa Travel is a private guide service based in Yerevan. We design personal day trips and multi-day journeys to Armenia's ancient monasteries, volcanic highlands, and hidden valleys — planned around you, and led by guides who grew up here.
        </p>

        <!-- Streamlined Minimal Highlights -->
        <div class="space-y-4">
